comments: Reddish (ATL) makes clean contact with the ball to deflect it away from Gordon (HOU) and then legally contests his jump shot attempt.
Augustin (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on Huerter (ATL) during his drive to the basket.
Huerter (ATL) places his off-arm against Augustin (HOU) but the contact is marginal.
Huerter (ATL) initiates contact with Gordon (HOU) that affects his FOM.
Capela (ATL) legally contests Tate's (HOU) dunk attempt at the rim.
Reddish (ATL) is already in Gordon's (HOU) path and marginal lower body contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Replay review of the foul called on Collins (ATL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful.  Sengun (HOU) is not in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Collins.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Following the marginal contact by Collins (ATL), Gordon (HOU) loses the ball out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Atlanta.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) and Collins (ATL) are both in a legal guarding position when Augustin (HOU) attempts to split the defenders
Young (ATL) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps to the basket.
Collins (ATL) attempts to commit a take foul on Tate (HOU), and the contact is marginal.
Huerter (ATL) moves underneath Gordon (HOU) and makes contact to his lower body as he receives the pass.
Gallinari (ATL) commits a take foul on Gordon (HOU).
